text.tspan: After many years as software developers, my associate and I decided to separate all Open Source libraries from all of our other companies to be able to create without any ties.
Our main focus is that our libraries must be highly secure, easily maintainable with great readability and code quality.
The icon was made from a 0 (zero) but adding a natural yet fiery aspect to it, symbolizing our intent to create solutions that are fresh, concise and meaningful.
The name was selected with a similar approach but also looking for something that sounded familiar and welcoming.
